{"tid":1702322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[記者朋友請入]又一實例證明 投訴警察課 完全無撚用","createTime":"2019-11-09T15:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T08:39:03.000Z","uid":103842,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6901515308b536149d4475af694fda0ec419f14d","tid":1702322,"uid":103842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"第一次 醫院毒打阿伯<br />\n投訴警察課既調查只係問左自己友有無做 跟住就話調查唔到 跟住close file <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔係病房有CCTV 果幾隻狗仲打緊其他人呀</span><br />\n第二次 少女係狗屋被輪姦<br />\n警方：接報有人在荃灣警署被強姦 指控與調查結果不吻合 跟住close file<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔係個女仔大左肚 先話俾你地記者聽有件咁既報案跟住話查緊</span><br />\n<br />\n我大膽假設 有超過一個女仔被姦/男仔被雞姦同超過一個受害者曾經報案投訴<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">到底有幾多單係投訴左跟住 投訴警察課話查唔到close左file?</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不過我估佢地都唔會話俾你地聽</span><br />\n<br />\n客觀既事實就係投訴警察課 根本無能力調查POPO既犯罪  <br />\n唔駛再係度尻UP咩監警會 監警會係阿伯被毒打件事上做過咩? 係少女被狗輪姦既事上做過咩?<br />\n必須重整整個制度!"},{"pid":"a904f6c8cae88248ace01c52f49334d1a7032f7c","tid":1702322,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:36:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b25823b60a0e8610f7fec7edea249e44869b6d6b","tid":1702322,"uid":103842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"49e1c6433b0ea253dd6adf0531dd75effd819d7b","tid":1702322,"uid":103842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"狗仔死全家"},{"pid":"5263375077ae2032793b5737fd0a6db6d87f0973","tid":1702322,"uid":103842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"ce9e80406647f8bd32acd6404749c4770d813253","tid":1702322,"uid":305837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:14:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"652de6c4aaeb6602c1f1af85ba440a3889d876e2","tid":1702322,"uid":235543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi